<TEXT>
<P>
 I'm sick of Woodstock. I hope the reunion is a financial disaster so we'll 
never see another one.With the Cal Jam and Us festivals, the 
six-figure-attendance rock extravaganzas have been done to death. But, just 
like the overpriced concert tours this summer, this anniversary has to be 
