every cent of the $12.50 I paid to see them in '79.) 
</P>
<P>
 Wood 
</P>
<P>
 ock, indeed. Hey, where can I get one of those hats? How about a T-shirt? 
Better yet, a personally designed limited-edition hand-painted 
bead-and-fringe-trimmed denim jacket for $400 from Neiman-Marcus . . . aargh! 
