<HEADLINE>
<P>
O.C. RELIGION NOTES / DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Rev. Jerry Seiden is the new pastor at Harbor Christian Fellowship in 
Costa Mesa.He has served congregations in Paramount and Ventura and was a 
chaplain for the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department. He is the author of 
several books, including "Divine or Distorted? God As We Understand God." He 
recently compiled and edited "The Positive Thinkers' New Testament and Psalms," 
a project for the Peale Center for Christian Living and the NationaL Publishing 
Company. 
</P>
<P>
 Sunday worship services are at 10 a.m. at 740 W. Wilson St. Information: (714) 
631-7730. 
</P>
