<P>
 The Rev. Ronald Gleason will give his first sermon as the new senior pastor of 
Covenant Presbyterian Church in Orange on Sunday.He served as a pastor in 
Toronto, Canada, for nine years after 10 years in The Netherlands before taking 
this position. 
</P>
