<TEXT>
<P>
 Cantor Jonathan Grant has joined the staff at Temple Bat Yahm of Newport 
Beach.He served as cantorial soloist at the Wilshire Boulevard Temple in Los 
Angeles for four years, then completed formal cantorial training at the Hebrew 
Union College Jewish Institute of Religion in New York. During his four years 
of study he served at the Brooklyn Heights Synagogue with Rabbi Sue Ann 
Wasserman. 
