has been hired as an assistant at Cal State Northridge. 
</P>
<P>
 Malisch, 30, guided the Griffins to a pair of St. Louis Intercollegiate 
Athletic Conference titles during her four seasons at the NCAA Division III 
school. 
</P>
<P>
 She is a 1986 graduate of Rockhurst College in Kansas City, Mo., where she was 
most valuable player as a junior and senior. 
